query:
SELECT s.id, s.firstName, s.lastName, s.beltRank, bp.currentBelt, bp.nextBelt, bp.progressPercent, bp.qualifiedAttendance 
FROM students s 
LEFT JOIN belt_progress bp ON s.id = bp.studentId 
LIMIT 10;
